--[[
	ACCESSORY EDITOR v4
	Tabs: Textures · Mesh Swap · Full Replace · Inspector · Live Feed
	
	Core philosophy:
	  - Never write directly to server-owned parts (goes black / ignored)
	  - For texture/mesh changes: clone the Handle, modify clone, swap it in
	  - For full replace: InsertService:LoadAsset → extract Accessory → weld in
	  - Live feed: GetPropertyChangedSignal + ChildAdded on every desc
--]]

